nsparent","index":"b4f","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Breaks Above ~5K msg\/sec Because...","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#FF7B72","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":482975451,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":28,"angle":0,"y":-1945,"width":295.50372314453125},{"seed":789154741,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"pDOEboVs4TczcrZYH6nbO","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"MySQL single primary hits I\/O saturation -> write latency spikes.\nRedis full-mesh fan-out: every server gets every message, even irrelevant ones.\nWebSocket FD limit: ~65K per process, memory-bound beyond that.\nNo horizontal scaling path — LB can't do sticky routing for WebSockets.\nFirst domino: MySQL write queue backs up and everything halts.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4g","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"MySQL single primary hits I\/O saturation -> write latency spikes.\nRedis full-mesh fan-out: every server gets every message, even irrelevant ones.\nWebSocket FD limit: ~65K per process, memory-bound beyond that.\nNo horizontal scaling path — LB can't do sticky routing for WebSockets.\nFirst domino: MySQL write queue backs up and everything halts.","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":625512533,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":28,"angle":0,"y":-1915,"width":537.66937255859375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#44475A","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4h","backgroundColor":"#161B22","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"mci2RT_WCTVhdZ4DPqw97","x":1023,"seed":2108181781,"boundElements":[],"y":-2311,"opacity":100,"height":670,"width":850,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":495389563},{"seed":27779701,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"Xdz0Hz_n58KTKVsAT2eXl","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Why Start Simple","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4i","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Why Start Simple","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#3FB950","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":719175093,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":-2289,"width":132.11187744140625},{"seed":2144193493,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"QNmohrhuCyADlbK5X3QaQ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"In a system design interview, establishing a baseline\nshows structured thinking: you know what a naive\nimplementation looks like and exactly why it fails.\nIt also anchors every subsequent complexity — when you\nadd Kafka or Cassandra later, the interviewer understands\nprecisely what problem each piece solves. Starting with\na 6-component monolith proves you don't over-engineer;\nyou scale only when forced to by a concrete bottleneck.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4j","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"In a system design interview, establishing a baseline\nshows structured thinking: you know what a naive\nimplementation looks like and exactly why it fails.\nIt also anchors every subsequent complexity — when you\nadd Kafka or Cassandra later, the interviewer understands\nprecisely what problem each piece solves. Starting with\na 6-component monolith proves you don't over-engineer;\nyou scale only when forced to by a concrete bottleneck.","height":140,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1227744283,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":-2263,"width":400.95953369140625},{"seed":137333045,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"7chpd696RWYgsY8oXfOpd","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"The Failure Cascade","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4k","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The Failure Cascade","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#FF7B72","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":338050837,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":-2119,"width":157.82383728027344},{"seed":204642965,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"yh7IK4HiSZfzj7iGhBU1Q","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Traffic climbs past 5K msg\/sec. MySQL's write buffer fills.\nInsert latency rises from 5ms to 200ms to 2s. Chat\nservers wait on the DB call — their async loops stall.\nWebSocket send buffers back up on each server. Clients\ntime out waiting for delivery confirmation and disconnect.\n50K clients disconnecting simultaneously is a thundering\nherd: all retry at once, hammering the load balancer.\nThe LB becomes the second bottleneck. New connections\nare refused. The system appears fully down to all users,\neven though the DB is the only component truly saturated.\nThis cascade, from DB write -> server stall -> client\ndisconnect -> LB storm, takes under 30 seconds.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4l","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Traffic climbs past 5K msg\/sec. MySQL's write buffer fills.\nInsert latency rises from 5ms to 200ms to 2s. Chat\nservers wait on the DB call — their async loops stall.\nWebSocket send buffers back up on each server. Clients\ntime out waiting for delivery confirmation and disconnect.\n50K clients disconnecting simultaneously is a thundering\nherd: all retry at once, hammering the load balancer.\nThe LB becomes the second bottleneck. New connections\nare refused. The system appears fully down to all users,\neven though the DB is the only component truly saturated.\nThis cascade, from DB write -> server stall -> client\ndisconnect -> LB storm, takes under 30 seconds.","height":210,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1471195323,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":-2093,"width":407.2454833984375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#D29922","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4m","backgroundColor":"#1a1000","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"IjWKAmBmIj1eNHmWSZ2z1","x":1028,"seed":881623029,"boundElements":[],"y":-1831,"opacity":100,"height":170,"width":840,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":932680821},{"seed":2000861525,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"u61FH6ei3rfgRwS35D6mn","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"What the V1 -> V2 Upgrade Must Fix","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4n","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"What the V1 -> V2 Upgrade Must Fix","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#D29922","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1588713819,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":-1813,"width":288.4637451171875},{"seed":1839908533,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"fEPx0mMTdSUTYRUk0KtoR","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"1. Replace MySQL with Cassandra (write-optimized, sharded)\n2. Replace Redis pub\/sub with Kafka (partitioned, durable)\n3. Add consistent-hash LB for sticky WebSocket routing\n4. Separate presence service (offload heartbeat writes)\n5. Add CDN + object store for media (remove from chat path)","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4o","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Replace MySQL with Cassandra (write-optimized, sharded)\n2. Replace Redis pub\/sub with Kafka (partitioned, durable)\n3. Add consistent-hash LB for sticky WebSocket routing\n4. Separate presence service (offload heartbeat writes)\n5. Add CDN + object store for media (remove from chat path)","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":16203221,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":-1787,"width":423.73748779296875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transparent","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4p","backgroundColor":"#111827","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":7,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"V65Vwu4-N5wd8eOi9Jq0d","x":-1007,"seed":1785341973,"boundElements":[],"y":-1541,"opacity":100,"height":100,"width":3000,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":461633019},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transparent","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4q","backgroundColor":"#0D1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":7,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"AKT3tZJ3aC7AdA7i4n48n","x":-1007,"seed":1333157237,"boundElements":[],"y":-1441,"opacity":100,"height":710,"width":3000,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1197128501},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transparent","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4r","backgroundColor":"#111827","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":7,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"Zepn4on9P9ILbkYPfgMaK","x":-1007,"seed":605349589,"boundElements":[],"y":-731,"opacity":100,"height":80,"width":3000,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":2099871387},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transparent","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4s","backgroundColor":"#161B22","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":7,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"KLeilgc1GlpiwJhIPNGmI","x":-1007,"seed":1792754741,"boundElements":[],"y":-1441,"opacity":100,"height":60,"width":3000,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1663536277},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transparent","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4t","backgroundColor":"#FF7B72","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":8,"roundness":null,"type":"ellipse","updated":1772977438387,"id":"ar866BTWSyXi5lnFOj9WW","x":-985,"seed":934213013,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"IZmiChC6SA8BTvIDfornE"}],"y":-1429,"opacity":100,"height":47,"width":36,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1851061051},{"seed":96828149,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"IZmiChC6SA8BTvIDfornE","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1772977438393,"locked":false,"text":"5","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4u","roundness":null,"containerId":"ar866BTWSyXi5lnFOj9WW","originalText":"5","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#0D1117","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":845884725,"textAlign":"center","fontF