:true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bFq","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Retry Formula","height":18.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#3FB950","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1236506965,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":4179,"width":102.34494018554688},{"seed":724315285,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"5jeATVAfdNW15uQq4N6b6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"wait = min(100ms x 2^n + rand(0,500ms), 32s)\nThe jitter (rand) is critical: without it, all\nclients that failed at T+0 retry simultaneously\nat T+100ms — a synchronized thundering herd.\nJitter breaks the synchrony. Max cap (32s) prevents\nclient UX degrading to minutes. After attempt 5:\nKafka messages -> messages.dlq topic.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bFr","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"wait = min(100ms x 2^n + rand(0,500ms), 32s)\nThe jitter (rand) is critical: without it, all\nclients that failed at T+0 retry simultaneously\nat T+100ms — a synchronized thundering herd.\nJitter breaks the synchrony. Max cap (32s) prevents\nclient UX degrading to minutes. After attempt 5:\nKafka messages -> messages.dlq topic.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":267195003,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":4203,"width":362.1375732421875},{"seed":579064309,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"rxSmm-wkVS30nSU2tzafa","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"DLQ Policy","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bFs","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"DLQ Policy","height":18.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#D29922","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2130683573,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":4317,"width":78.929946899414062},{"seed":243256149,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"39UjFiTu5NwwbbU4vma99","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Trigger: 5 failed retries -> messages.dlq topic.\nAlert: PagerDuty fires when DLQ depth > 10\nmessages in 5 minutes.\nOps procedure: inspect payload (corrupt? dependency\ndown?), fix root cause, replay with consumer group\nreset to DLQ offset. Messages retained 7 days.\nNever auto-replay without manual inspection.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bFt","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Trigger: 5 failed retries -> messages.dlq topic.\nAlert: PagerDuty fires when DLQ depth > 10\nmessages in 5 minutes.\nOps procedure: inspect payload (corrupt? dependency\ndown?), fix root cause, replay with consumer group\nreset to DLQ offset. Messages retained 7 days.\nNever auto-replay without manual inspection.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":792398619,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":4341,"width":360.82159423828125},{"seed":2138413237,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"7H087_kfxMOJrVuD1CdvW","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Idempotency Implementation","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bFu","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Idempotency Implementation","height":18.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#58A6FF","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1042483221,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":4463,"width":207.32987976074219},{"seed":1594538517,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"IJulLwXGxAcBjFWli4zuQ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Two-layer dedup: Redis (network layer) + TIMEUUID\n(storage layer). Redis handles the common case:\nclient retries due to timeout. TTL=24h covers all\nreasonable retry windows. TIMEUUID handles the\nrare case where Redis itself fails between GET and\nSET — Cassandra's PK uniqueness absorbs the\nduplicate insert silently (upsert semantics).","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bFv","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Two-layer dedup: Redis (network layer) + TIMEUUID\n(storage layer). Redis handles the common case:\nclient retries due to timeout. TTL=24h covers all\nreasonable retry windows. TIMEUUID handles the\nrare case where Redis itself fails between GET and\nSET — Cassandra's PK uniqueness absorbs the\nduplicate insert silently (upsert semantics).","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1870720955,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":4487,"width":365.66558837890625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transparent","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bFw","backgroundColor":"#0D1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"lDq_NMXoiQTCQNpLHxmct","x":-1007,"seed":1177857909,"boundElements":[],"y":4809,"opacity":100,"height":540,"width":3000,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":2031304053},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"transpar