signed URLs, chat server bypassed","height":16.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":446638453,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-427,"angle":0,"y":5853,"width":413.99758911132812},{"seed":1582682325,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"G6tm_yPau6rjqMlRVA8eI","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Multi-region: Cassandra async geo-replication, GLB health checks","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bGz","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Multi-region: Cassandra async geo-replication, GLB health checks","height":16.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1096422491,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-427,"angle":0,"y":5875,"width":409.30450439453125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#44475A","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bH0","backgroundColor":"#161B22","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772977438387,"id":"O0yAUv_2pa3gNVDbxbn5p","x":1023,"seed":1097788981,"boundElements":[],"y":5499,"opacity":100,"height":500,"width":850,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":675558101},{"seed":306012053,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"ALkqD5CkseKYZf9UOXxv8","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"30-Second Verbal Summary","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bH1","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"30-Second Verbal Summary","height":18.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#58A6FF","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":325898491,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":5517,"width":191.369873046875},{"seed":385262837,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"rvgLlh_zqekTsghGJfPwl","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"The core challenge in chat is real-time push\ncombined with durable persistence at scale.\nMy design uses WebSocket Gateways with\nconsistent-hash routing for stateful connections,\nKafka partitioned by conversation ID for ordered\nfan-out, and Cassandra for write-optimized storage.\nPresence uses Redis TTL keys, eliminating 333K\nDB writes\/sec from heartbeats. Media is offloaded\nvia pre-signed S3 URLs. Result: 500K msg\/sec,\n<100ms P99, 99.99% availability via active-passive\nmulti-region with ~90s RTO.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bH2","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The core challenge in chat is real-time push\ncombined with durable persistence at scale.\nMy design uses WebSocket Gateways with\nconsistent-hash routing for stateful connections,\nKafka partitioned by conversation ID for ordered\nfan-out, and Cassandra for write-optimized storage.\nPresence uses Redis TTL keys, eliminating 333K\nDB writes\/sec from heartbeats. Media is offloaded\nvia pre-signed S3 URLs. Result: 500K msg\/sec,\n<100ms P99, 99.99% availability via active-passive\nmulti-region with ~90s RTO.","height":192.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1128337461,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":5541,"width":357.90960693359375},{"seed":857751125,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"F_sCPGliE3jxxFSCzMfih","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Senior vs Staff Answer","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bH3","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Senior vs Staff Answer","height":18.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#D29922","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1497299355,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":5719,"width":168.7498779296875},{"seed":1032825781,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"4h7DEKxy0aerPeM8eIiDB","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772977438387,"locked":false,"text":"Senior: Designs correct system. Knows Cassandra\nbeats MySQL for writes. Adds Kafka for fan-out.\nHandles WebSocket routing with consistent hash.\n\nStaff: Quantifies the presence write storm\n(333K writes\/sec). Explains TIMEUUID vs TIMESTAMP\nand why both matter. Discusses fan-out push vs pull\nthreshold (switch at >10K group members). Knows\nwhen active-passive vs active-active trade is worth\nmaking. Names the binding constraint (WebSocket\nstate) before being asked.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bH4","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Senior: Designs correct system. Knows Cassandra\nbeats MySQL for writes. Adds Kafka for fan-out.\nHandles WebSocket routing with consistent hash.\n\nStaff: Quantifies the presence write storm\n(333K writes\/sec). Explains TIMEUUID vs TIMESTAMP\nand why both matter. Discusses fan-out push vs pull\nthreshold (switch at >10K group members). Knows\nwhen active-passive vs active-active trade is worth\nmaking. Names the binding constraint (WebSocket\nstate) before being asked.","height":192.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#F8F8F2","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":427508117,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1048,"angle":0,"y":5743,"width":387.967529296875}],"version